Candidate spellings follow EC spelling standards. There is conflicting information on how many direct candidates (no party affiliation with GRS Coalition) GRS has. GRS had an initial electoral pact with PH to avoid seat overlap but they clashed for this election. BN had an initial electoral pact with PH to prevent seat overlaps but they clashed for this elections. STAR and SAPP have an electoral pact (hence they are parked in Other Party (1) Category.  Around 17 independent candidates are part of the Black Wave Movement. On 17th November 2025, PKR candidate Hj. Abdul Halim Sidek bin Gulam Hassan withdrew from the contest.
